During the course, the students will finalize the portfolio, providing evidence of their professional competence in six areas: planning the learning process, design the learning environment, supporting learning and learner development, reflection and professional self-development and developing the image of vocational education.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To support the vocational teacher students in creating the vocational teacher development portfolio.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Student: 1) prepares a digital development portfolio structured on the basis of the competences listed in the professional standard of vocational teacher, level 6; 2) selects appropriate evidence to demonstrate competences; 3) explains the structure of portfolio.
